definitions.definition: A person who is presented (e.g. to a benefice ), or to whom an award is given.
One who is present at work , especially if too sick to be productive , or working beyond the expected hours .

main_definition: A person who is presented (e.g. to a benefice ), or to whom an award is given.
secondary_definitions: One who is present at work , especially if too sick to be productive , or working beyond the expected hours . [from 20th c.]
